        "\n",
        "**Problem Statement:**\n",
        "\n",
        "Customer churn (when customers leave a service) is a major revenue killer for telecom companies. Manually identifying which customers are at risk of leaving is impossible at scale. We need an automated, production-ready system that can process raw customer data and predict churn accurately.\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "**Objective:**  \n",
        "\n",
        "Build a reusable and production-ready machine learning pipeline for predicting customer churn. Specifically, this project involves:\n",
        "\n",
        "* Loading the Telco Churn Dataset.\n",
        "\n",
        "* Implementing data preprocessing steps (scaling, encoding) using Scikit-Learn's Pipeline.\n",
        "\n",
        "* Training a machine learning model (Random Forest).\n",
        "\n",
        "* Using GridSearchCV for hyperparameter tuning to find the best model parameters.\n",
        "\n",
        "* Exporting the complete, trained pipeline using joblib for future reusability."
      ],
